  "counters": [],
  "npcs": [
    {
      "name": "Shelly the Intern",
      "x": 20,
      "y": 9,
      "sprite": "Actor3",
      "sprite_index": 3,
      "step_anime": true,
      "facing": "down",
      "wander": false,
      "through": false,
      "dialogue": {
        "speaker": "Shelly the Intern",
        "portrait": "Actor3",
        "face_index": 3,
        "lines": [
          "These guys aren't paying me enough. They aren't paying me anything!",
          "The Boss brought in a new developer metrics tool to figure out our quality problems...",
          "He berated me for my mean time to review metric. So Leah stamps all my commits now to keep him happy."
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "Leah Dev",
      "x": 5,
      "y": 5,
      "sprite": "SF_Actor2",
      "sprite_index": 3,
      "step_anime": true,
      "facing": "down",
      "wander": false,
      "through": false,
      "dialogue": {
        "speaker": "Leah Dev",
        "portrait": "SF_Actor2",
        "face_index": 3,
        "lines": [
          "I can't take it anymore! Can I tell you a secret?",
          "I'm interviewing around so I can have a life again.",
          "Tenex breaks things all the time and refuses to add distributed tracing every time I ask.",
          "Every incident is like hunting for a needle in infinite haystacks. I like to imagine their faces when I resign."
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "New Guy",
      "x": 20,
      "y": 16,
      "sprite": "SF_Actor1",
      "sprite_index": 4,
      "step_anime": true,
      "facing": "left",
      "wander": false,
      "through": false,
      "dialogue": {
        "speaker": "Kirito",
        "portrait": "SF_Actor1",
        "face_index": 4,
        "lines": [
          "I started here months ago and it's like this isekai I watched where the guy has no powers and the starting town hates him.",
          "I really need to hit a year at this place or my resume's look terrible.",
          "Maybe I can transfer to Team Marathon but they almost never have openings."
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "Tenex",
      "x": 8,
      "y": 14,
      "sprite": "Monster",
      "sprite_index": 1,
      "step_anime": true,
      "facing": "down",
      "wander": false,
      "through": false,
      "dialogue": {
        "speaker": "Tenex",
        "portrait": "Monster",
        "face_index": 1,
        "lines": [
          "I worked 100 hours last week. I get free food here so why would I go home?",
          "Oh, that incident? I told those nerds in Team Disco that I was reading their tables.",
          "They said something about schema changes blah blah blah but I zoned out."
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "The Boss",
      "x": 14,
      "y": 14,
      "sprite": "Monster",
      "sprite_index": 7,
      "step_anime": true,
      "facing": "down",
      "wander": false,
      "through": false,
      "dialogue": {
        "speaker": "The Boss",
        "portrait": "Monster",
        "face_index": 3,
        "lines": [
          "These darn Millenials don't want to work. When I was a lad we wrote COBOL and we hustled and look at me! I turned out fine.",
          "The security bots are on my case about so-called vulnerabilities. I threatened the team with termination if they write bugs, so that's fixed."
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "Merc",
      "x": 17,
      "y": 5,
      "sprite": "SF_Actor3",
      "sprite_index": 2,
      "step_anime": true,
      "facing": "down",
      "wander": false,
      "through": false,
      "dialogue": {
        "speaker": "Merc",
        "portrait": "SF_Actor3",
        "face_index": 2,
        "lines": [
          "I just go with the flow. I get paid either way so who am I to complain? My rate's the same for nonsense as it is for good work."
        ]
      }
    }
  ],
